  "title": "Centre Support",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assists Educator to monitor and supervisors the children in the classroom, on field trips, meal times and other activities; or may monitor the class when Educator is otherwise occupied with parents</li>\n  <li>Assists in providing routine care such as transition, bathing, feeding, diapering, toileting, dressing and napping and must be familiar with the steps and procedures in carrying out the routine care</li>\n  <li>Ensures that the environment is clean, safe and healthy</li>\n  <li>Assists in health check, visual screening and temperature taking</li>\n  <li>Performs cook or cleaner duties whenever necessary</li>\n</ul>",
